            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "FS19 is a great medium level farming game compared to the latest available. Tons to do with plenty of automations possible. Be careful not to tax the Giants 8 programming by running too many simultaneous AI workers (3 harvesters max with 3 auger wagons). The more AutoDrive command clicks the quicker the game will freeze. Just be aware. Take your time and you'll enjoy the game. Tons of mods (some less polished than others)."
        },
